        {
            "title": "香港國際7人欖球賽｜新西蘭男女隊力爭香港站三連霸",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"新西蘭男女隊力爭香港站三連霸。AP\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f430558f3ce240dc4e6f6d43fce10379/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250327/_2025032719105237175.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">新西蘭男女隊力爭香港站三連霸。AP</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>世界七人欖球系列賽第5站的香港國際七人欖球賽，男、女子隊各12支核心球隊周五早上10時半在全新的啟德主場館進行首天共24埸比賽，新西蘭男、女子隊若成功衛冕，就能同時成為香港站「三連霸」。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"新西蘭女子隊(白衫)力爭香港站三連霸。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/224453438292785f74d3d0fe233987a2/2025-03/Olympics_Rugby_New_Zealand_Woodman_Wickliffe_15092--58f47.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        新西蘭女子隊(白衫)力爭香港站三連霸。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"香港國際7人欖球賽周五在啟德主場館開打。何君健攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3852a8890ae68cd5efa91812dd5458c2/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-27_at_4_00_50_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        香港國際7人欖球賽周五在啟德主場館開打。何君健攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"法國男隊是巴黎奧運金牌得主。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/10811a453b1e9247a890cd4279e0bd8e/2025-03/2024-11-07T110335Z_1511606240_RC2U39AB5EV9_RTRMADP_3_RUGBY-UNION-FRA-JAP_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        法國男隊是巴黎奧運金牌得主。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"新西蘭是上屆冠軍。美聯社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/855a1d83d2767837faab1e716702d777/2025-03/Hong_Kong_Rugby_Sevens_84766--30df0_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        新西蘭是上屆冠軍。美聯社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"新西蘭是上屆冠軍。美聯社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5d593837f5ddd8bf62f18e2b9bd1f07b/2025-03/AFP_34NU7LW_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        新西蘭是上屆冠軍。美聯社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"香港男子隊(藍衫)上屆在銀劍賽決賽勝日本隊。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f6181ab94dd5fb16bcec8e8790dc6ae9/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-27_at_3_54_09_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        香港男子隊(藍衫)上屆在銀劍賽決賽勝日本隊。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"莊嘉欣(中)去年銀劍賽決賽鬥中國隊。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/05312d5eb050f55e33c9fb881c494204/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-27_at_4_04_50_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        莊嘉欣(中)去年銀劍賽決賽鬥中國隊。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"隊長蔡紀駿（右一）首次出任香港國際七人欖球賽港隊隊長，左一為首次入選的19歲紀遠恆。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a80652f0a3a929139402aa6ecbf72e46/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-27_at_3_23_48_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        隊長蔡紀駿（右一）首次出任香港國際七人欖球賽港隊隊長，左一為首次入選的19歲紀遠恆。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"蔡紀駿上屆銀劍賽決賽力拒日本隊。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/24a9b90b7e8011fc47c91d61e13844e8/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-27_at_3_51_55_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        蔡紀駿上屆銀劍賽決賽力拒日本隊。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"香港國際7人欖球賽周五在啟德主場館開打。何君健攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/863fe4890922dbd63acf4376f1433c32/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-26_at_10_12_01_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        香港國際7人欖球賽周五在啟德主場館開打。何君健攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"香港國際7人欖球賽周五在啟德主場館開打。何君健攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6539af0cd97b2aed0c90421256ad6787/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-26_at_8_55_44_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        香港國際7人欖球賽周五在啟德主場館開打。何君健攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>巴黎奧運女子組金牌的新西蘭隊，其隊長夏雲妮（Sarah Hirini)周三到啟德出席隊長合照後表示：「很驕傲能成為啟德主場館第一項國際賽事，感覺草地是一個快場，上蓋能開合簡直難以置信。」新隊同組有中國國家隊、巴西及美國。\n\n</p><h2>新西蘭男隊圖於香港站開齋</h2>\n<p>新西蘭男隊去年巴奧8強爆冷負南非，隊長哥利亞（Dylan Collier)預示新場氣氛更勝大球場，亦談到己隊說：「自巴奧後，我隊在球員及管理層都作出大調動，需要時間去磨合，今季幾站都未贏過冠軍，很想在香港站爭取『三連冠』。」新西蘭男子隊同組有宿敵南非、澳洲及烏拉圭。\n\n</p>\n<p>男、女子組各分3組比賽，小組頭2名及2隊小組最佳第3名入8強淘汰賽，在香港有19勝紀錄的斐濟身處A組，巴黎奧運男子組金牌的法國隊跟西班牙、英格蘭及肯亞同組。完成頭4站比賽，阿根廷及新西蘭暫列男、女子組排名第一位。\n\n</p>\n<p>記者：徐嘉華\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
